h1. shiro:isNotLoggedIn

h2. Purpose
Conditionally render the contents of the tag if the current user NOT authenticated.

h2. Examples
{code}
<shiro:isNotLoggedIn>
    <span>
           Please sign in <input name="username"/> <input type="password" name="password"/>
    </span>
    ...
</shiro:isNotLoggedIn>


{code}

h2. Description
This tag only writes its body to the output if the user is NOT authenticate, defers to SecurityUtils.subject.authenticated. (inversion of [isLoggedIn|Tags])



